        <span class="tool-tag">Looker</span>
        <span class="tool-tag">Excel</span>
        <span class="tool-tag">GCP</span>
        <span class="tool-tag">MySQL</span>
        <span class="tool-tag">ETL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EXPERIENCE -->
<section id="experience">
  <div class="section-label">Career Timeline</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Work <em>Experience</em></h2>

  <div class="exp-grid">

    <div class="exp-left">
      <div class="exp-date">Sep 2025 — Present</div>
      <div class="exp-company">NxtWave</div>
    </div>
    <div class="exp-right">
      <div class="exp-role">Data Analyst</div>
      <ul class="exp-bullets">
        <li>Built <strong>10+ Power BI dashboards</strong> with DAX measures tracking real-time KPIs used by senior leadership daily.</li>
        <li>Wrote complex SQL (CTEs, Window Functions, Joins) in <strong>Google BigQuery</strong> analyzing 1M+ record datasets.</li>
        <li>Reduced data pipeline errors by <strong>~30%</strong> through data cleaning and validation across 5+ reporting pipelines.</li>
        <li>Created <strong>STTM documents</strong> and transformation logic; managed end-to-end ETL workflows.</li>
        <li>Built <strong>Google Looker Studio</strong> dashboards for 3+ business teams with full data definitions.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr class="exp-divider">

